'''性代理人'''（{{lang-en|'''sexual surrogate'''}}），有时称作'''替身性伴侣'''，是[[性治疗|性治疗]]团队的一员，指导[[治疗师|治疗师]]并进行代理。<ref name="#1">{{cite web| url = http://www.aolhealth.com/healthy-living/relationships/sex-surrogate| last = Burford| first = Michelle| title = Is a Sex Surrogate Right for You?| work = AOL Health| date = September 2009| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100212024319/http://www.aolhealth.com/healthy-living/relationships/sex-surrogate| archivedate = 2010年2月12日| deadurl = yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Surrogate Partner Therapy|author=International Professional Surrogates Association|url=http://www.surrogatetherapy.org/what-is-surrogate-partner-therapy/|accessdate=13 March 2013|archive-date=2021-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210131004259/https://www.surrogatetherapy.org/what-is-surrogate-partner-therapy|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="#2">{{cite web |url=http://www.womenshealthmag.com/sex-and-relationships/sex-surrogate |title=Better-Sex Secrets from a Sex Surrogate | Women's Health Magazine |publisher=Womenshealthmag.com |date=2012-10-15 |accessdate=2014-03-03 |archive-date=2014-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141016054232/http://www.womenshealthmag.com/sex-and-relationships/sex-surrogate |dead-url=no }}</ref> 有些夫妇一同参加性代理环节，而有些人（单身或夫妇之一）会独自参加性代理。<ref name="#2"/> 代理人通过教育并与病人发生亲密肉体关系或[[人类性行为|性关系]]来达到治疗目标。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://womenshealthmag.com/sex-and-relationships/sex-surrogate |title=Better-Sex Secrets from a Sex Surrogate | Women's Health Magazine |publisher=Womenshealthmag.com |date=2012-10-15 |accessdate=2014-03-03 |archive-date=2014-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141016054232/http://www.womenshealthmag.com/sex-and-relationships/sex-surrogate |dead-url=no }}</ref> 这种做法由[[麥斯特與強生|玛斯特约翰逊研究所]]1970年出版的[[教科書|教科書]]《人类性功能失调》引入。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.zurinstitute.com/surrogate_partner_therapy.html |title=Surrogate Partner Therapy/Sexual Surrogacy-To Refer Or Not to Refer |publisher=Zurinstitute.com |date= |accessdate=2014-03-03 |archive-date=2019-01-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190117113019/http://www.zurinstitute.com/surrogate_partner_therapy.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

大部分代理人是女性<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ashvegas.com/new-ashvegas-feature-ask-the-sex-coach |title=New Ashvegas feature: Ask the Sex Coach |publisher=Ashvegas.com |date=2009-09-24 |accessdate=2014-03-03 |archive-date=2019-12-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191223194059/https://ashvegas.com/new-ashvegas-feature-ask-the-sex-coach |dead-url=no }}</ref>；也有一些是男性，<ref>DeHaan, Jerry De. ''Reaching Intimacy: A Male Sex Surrogate's Perspective'', published 1986.</ref> 并有已婚夫妇一起从事性代理工作。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://sexsurrogateofla.com/certified-sex-surrogate-partners.php |title=Certified Sex Surrogate Partners |publisher=Sexsurrogateofla.com |date= |accessdate=2014-03-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140303193336/http://sexsurrogateofla.com/certified-sex-surrogate-partners.php |archivedate=2014年3月3日 |df= }}</ref> 有些代理人就职于咨询中心，有些则有自己的办公室。除性代理之外，有些代理人还提供额外服务，例如电话咨询和[[性學|性學]]身体接触。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.informedaboutsex.com/a%20Sex%20Therapy.html |title=Sex Therapy |publisher=Informedaboutsex.com |date= |accessdate=2014-03-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140303192640/http://www.informedaboutsex.com/a%20Sex%20Therapy.html |archivedate=2014-03-03 }}</ref>

虽然任何人都可以在没有培训或认证下就称自己是（性）代理人，但这方面确实是有培训和专业认证的。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://al-hikmah.org/sex-surrogates-alternative-type-of-therapy.htm |title=Sex surrogates: an alternative type of therapy |publisher=http://al-hikmah.org |date=unknown (2004-2011) |accessdate=2014-03-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070405062446/http://www.al-hikmah.org/sex-surrogates-alternative-type-of-therapy.htm |archivedate=2007-04-05 }}</ref><ref name="#3">{{cite web |url=http://www.surrogatetherapy.org |title=IPSA |publisher=Surrogatetherapy.org |date= |accessdate=2014-03-03 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112012130/https://www.surrogatetherapy.org/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 国际专业代理协会，成立于1971，培训和认证性代理人，以及引导患者和治疗师向他们求助，还参加学术研究和公共教育。<ref name="#3"/><ref>{{cite web|last=Muller |first=Robert |url=http://www.psychologytoday.com/blog/talking-about-trauma/201305/sexual-surrogates-help-many-who-suffer-alone |title=Sexual Surrogates Help Many Who Suffer Alone |publisher=Psychology Today |date=2013-05-27 |accessdate=2014-03-03}}</ref> Vena Blanchard是其主席。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.venablanchard.com/About_Vena.html|title=About Vena|publisher=http://www.venablanchard.com|date=|accessdate=2014-03-03|archive-date=2019-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190905223126/http://venablanchard.com/About_Vena.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==典型问题==
病人常有以下特定问题：

{{col-begin}}{{col-break}}
* 亲密关系障碍
* 缺乏自信
* 沟通问题
* 约会焦虑
* [[性抑制|性抑制]]
{{col-break|gap=4em}}
* [[勃起功能障碍|阳痿]]
* [[早發性射精|早泄]]
* 疾病引起的性交疼痛，如[[陰道痙攣|陰道痙攣]]
{{col-end}}

有些人因为获得性[[身心障礙|失能]]（事故、瘫痪、疾病、创伤）改变了性生活方式。性代理人可以帮助他们发掘和发展性潜能。性功能障碍的起因是多种多样的，因此代理人使用的手段也各有不同。

==治疗==
由于许多性问题是心理的，而非生理的，所以在治疗过程中病人与代理人之间、代理人与临床专家之间，沟通都扮演着关键角色。代理人通过治疗训练帮助病人。这些可能包括{{le|放松技巧|relaxation techniques}}、亲密交流、教学[[软技能|社交技巧]]，和一些性接触。<ref>{{cite web|title=surrogate partner therapy|url=http://www.surrogatetherapy.org/what-is-surrogate-partner-therapy/|work=IPSA: INTERNATIONAL PROFESSIONAL SURROGATES ASSOCIATION|accessdate=27 January 2014|archive-date=2021-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210131004259/https://www.surrogatetherapy.org/what-is-surrogate-partner-therapy|dead-url=no}}</ref>  性代理人和密宗性教育家马尔西蒙说她和患者之间很少发生亲密的身体接触，她不会与那些与有伴侣关系的人性交。<ref name="#1"/>

